text: Maquet in 2018 Jacqueline Maquet (born May 13, 1949) is a member of the National Assembly of France. She represents the Pas-de-Calais department, and is a member of La République En Marche!, formerly a deputy for the Socialist Party. ==References== Category:1949 births Category:Living people Category:Women members of the National Assembly (France) Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 15th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:21st-century French women politicians Category:Socialist Party (France) politicians Category:La République En Marche! politicians
